"        <br /><br />\n"
"        Any processing performed by any of our third-party service providers "
"(“Recipients”) will, where required by law, be governed by a data processing "
"agreement in the form required by law, preserving any and all of your "
"statutory data protection rights and obligating the Recipients to respect "
