"\n"
"        <h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold my-2\">Disclosure of Your Personal "
"Data</h3>\n"
"        <h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold my-2\">Business Transactions</h3>\n"
"        If the Company is involved in a merger, acquisition, or asset sale, "
